{
  "stem": "7160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we arrive in Germany, after we crossed, I don't know, Poland, Ukraine, I don't know what countries we crossed walking, after 17 or 18 days walking.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, they took us to Dachau on the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How many people started on the walk?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think about 23,000, I hear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived, 1,700.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of them died on the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrive in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was heaven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had toilets, showers, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dachau?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Showers, toilets, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of people, officers, over there from different countries, so war prisoners, with stars here, with uniform.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which place is that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't even know what's Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After a while, I find out, you know, it was Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So over there, by the kitchen, was carrots and potatoes and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to sneak in, take a carrot, a potato.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I start eating them from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not as bad as Auschwitz and Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After we stay there for a few days, probably a week or two, they took us from there in another place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 11 camps, Camp 1 till 11, different camps, about two or three miles apart from each other, concentration camps, working camps, We had to clear out forests.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one was near Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The city was near Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah, I think that's the name of the city, the closest city that was to the camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all forests around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us to chop trees down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That way, they can make a road toward-- the tractors and all of those things can go through there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not as bad as Birkenau, but there was not very much food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
